      <guid>http://alicez.ink/post/%E5%B9%B3%E5%BA%B8%E7%9A%84%E5%B9%B3%E5%BA%B8%E7%9A%84%E6%81%B6/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;题记&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;And earthly power doth then show likest Gods&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;When mercy seasons justice&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;That in the course of justice none of us&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Should see salvation. We do pray for mercy,&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;And that same prayer doth teach us all to render&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The deeds of mercy&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&#34;right&#34;&gt;——The Merchant of Venice, Act IV, Scene I&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    
